Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:10.78,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.94,0:06:14.18,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to the market for the materials and then return to my workshop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.54,0:06:16.18,Default,Miriam,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:18.19,Default,Miriam,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that she will be elated. {TLCed, literally "child", referring to her cat. It's understood.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:21.48,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see your cat too. {I want to see HER cat too... -nt}{TLCed, Japanese people seldom use "you", it's considered impolite. Minette is speaking to Miriam, so no problems}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.92,0:06:25.40,Default,Miriam,0000,0000,0000,,Well... That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,0:06:32.79,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Monte, I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.20,0:06:38.18,Default,Monte,0000,0000,0000,,Search start. Locating documents{literature/books} related to the ancient Artifact.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.27,0:06:49.93,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Additonal keyword: Waterwheel of Heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.93,0:06:54.77,Default,Monte,0000,0000,0000,,Command accepted; locating documents related to "Waterwheel of Heavens".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:11.83,Default,Monte,0000,0000,0000,,Search completed. No documents relating to "Waterwheel of Heavens" can be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:15.83,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,It's indeed not easy to find.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:40.01,Default,Miriam,0000,0000,0000,,We sure bought quite a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.31,0:07:44.07,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, basically all that's needed is here. What's left is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.64,0:07:48.78,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,This is Salsa and Ritos' Clan, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.03,0:07:55.08,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Tortilla Co. has some of the most unique Crystals and supplements, unavailable on the market.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.58,0:07:56.97,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly. {TLCed, She said "this is most definitely true" which shortens to "exactly"}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.26,0:08:00.46,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon, Ritos.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:02.23,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.82,0:08:04.69,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me today?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:06.53,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,Or do you want me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.94,0:08:10.10,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,Or do you desire me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.65,0:08:12.83,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,"Want me"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.69,0:08:18.25,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here today for a Crystal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:18.91,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go, this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:22.16,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,You're just as always, ignoring without interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.46,0:08:23.44,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.55,0:08:25.30,Default,Miriam,0000,0000,0000,,They are used to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.61,0:08:27.91,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Ritos is always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.15,0:08:29.77,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon, Minette-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.97,0:08:31.31,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,And who might this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.42,0:08:34.97,Default,Miriam,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, I'm Miriam.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.41,0:08:37.31,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,How courteous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.79,0:08:40.67,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,I have some delicious stuff, want to come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.80,0:08:43.15,Default,Miriam,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.34,0:08:47.76,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Dad always says "When a stranger tells you there's delicious stuff and want you to follow, you mustn't go."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.89,0:08:49.75,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's a good girl Minette.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.16,0:08:51.41,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,You've been raised well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.91,0:08:55.17,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,Well then... I've a funny sister to play with, want to come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.69,0:08:58.21,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.28,0:09:00.02,Default,Miriam,0000,0000,0000,,Is that fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:04.48,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,So then, I'll go and get the Crystal while you guys rest at the lobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:06.15,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, sorry to bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.96,0:09:07.95,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Salsa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.04,0:09:09.02,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.07,0:09:13.16,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Leicester, Minette and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.62,0:09:14.64,Default,Miriam,0000,0000,0000,,It's Miriam.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.15,0:09:19.76,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really glad all of you came on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:21.39,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,What would you like to drink? You want something right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.91,0:09:23.22,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.22,0:09:24.35,Default,Miriam,0000,0000,0000,,That's fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Golem!{added this, BE SURE TO TLC IT OMGOMGOMG -masat}{Golem}{TLCed}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.51,0:09:30.28,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking about taking a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.44,0:09:32.88,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,This is a specially spiked tea with sleep medicine by Nee-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.07,0:09:35.18,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,I did not! Stop sprouting nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.60,0:09:36.75,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't spike it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.03,0:09:43.88,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,If you did, you can do things like this~ and that~ to Leicester while he's asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:45.78,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,Does it feel good here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.37,0:09:47.07,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,That place is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.57,0:09:50.41,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Salsa, it's weird if you remain silent at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.47,0:09:55.16,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,No Leicester, I was thinking only a little about it, only a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.41,0:09:57.64,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to have thought about it from that expression. {TLCed}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.52,0:10:02.01,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,Leicester-san, the Crystal that you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:05.29,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, you're reliable as expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:05.98,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.18,0:10:08.67,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,Do look for us if you have problems next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.95,0:10:10.76,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,You can still visit even if you don't have anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:13.79,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for not being able to properly tend to all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.07,0:10:17.08,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,But you really have a funny sister to play with.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.08,0:10:18.98,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,You told her something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:20.48,Default,Ritos,0000,0000,0000,,Well it's the truth, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.94,0:10:24.34,Default,Salsa,0000,0000,0000,,It's indeed better than being described as a boring sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.81,0:10:27.39,Default,Miriam,0000,0000,0000,,They are very funny people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.49,0:10:28.82,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.42,0:10:36.10,Default,Tango,0000,0000,0000,,Agnes, didn't we look here before?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.32,0:10:37.89,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.08,0:10:43.84,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,But there could be some things we left out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.12,0:10:56.04,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,This is... really nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.36,0:10:58.87,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,We took this photograph to commemorate the completion of Minette.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.13,0:11:02.87,Default,Tango,0000,0000,0000,,Woah, that was when Aberdeen started to have that indifferent look on his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.20,0:11:04.77,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.74,0:11:07.68,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Aber-nii! Avril!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.12,0:11:09.23,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.80,0:11:13.42,Default,Roland,0000,0000,0000,,I need Minette's core, only that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.58,0:11:19.78,Default,Tango,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly is going on with Aberdeen and Avril?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.29,0:11:22.79,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,It won't change anything even if we are puzzled.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.04,0:11:25.35,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,They must have some circumstances of their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:28.84,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Aber-nii isn't the type who would say such things on a whim. {Unreasonably/without a reason}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.27,0:11:30.33,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Same with Avril...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.44,0:11:32.50,Default,Tango,0000,0000,0000,,Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.73,0:11:38.81,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, what we need to do now is to find leads to the Waterwheel of Heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.45,0:11:41.53,Default,Tango,0000,0000,0000,,I see, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.91,0:11:44.72,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Maitresse must also be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.32,0:11:48.02,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, I'll catch up right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:11:57.58,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about the mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.69,0:12:01.11,Default,Miriam,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm really excited to be seeing unknown things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.86,0:12:06.74,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Papa is able to do anything, but just doesn't clean up his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.14,0:12:11.17,Default,Miriam,0000,0000,0000,,I see, he's the same type as my brother. {You can already guess who her brother is}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.24,0:12:14.14,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even find any excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.29,0:12:19.99,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,You can sit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.26,0:12:21.85,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Is Papa standing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.10,0:12:23.82,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Well, since it's rather crammed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.23,0:12:26.77,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll sit together with Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.11,0:12:35.23,Default,Miriam,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you really get along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.61,0:12:44.74,Default,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,A disaster is about to strike Ert'Aria again. {Well, I used catastrophe, but to suit the title, let's use disaster}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.21,0:12:55.15,Default,Chel,0000,0000,0000,,Goddess, please bestow me with power to protect my beloved people in Ert'Aria.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.66,0:13:01.36,Default,Chel,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, where this is place?! {Where am I?!} {TLCed}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.34,0:13:17.95,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.70,0:13:20.87,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.26,0:13:22.37,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,How's the situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.62,0:13:26.83,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,I looked through the entire library of books in the Verritti house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:30.52,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,I still can't find any documents related to the Waterwheel of Heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.80,0:13:32.09,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:36.12,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking of going to other places to search.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.30,0:13:39.91,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,My... What's with the noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.16,0:13:43.05,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Miriam-san came over to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.45,0:13:45.88,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Minette-chan's friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.33,0:13:49.14,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,They sound really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.41,0:13:52.85,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Minette-san and Miriam-san are very close.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.17,0:13:59.29,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,That child is friendly with anyone, but she's particularly close to Miriam-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.49,0:14:06.56,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,She also said that she has a sort of comfortable feeling when she's with Miriam-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.79,0:14:08.10,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.35,0:14:10.55,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Their personalities are completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.86,0:14:13.75,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.41,0:14:18.30,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,No, the way you talk about Minette-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.71,0:14:22.99,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like you're talking about your real daughter or sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.83,0:14:26.87,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh dear... It's not just Minette-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.53,0:14:34.06,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Leicester, Annie-chan, Chel-san, Nick and also you, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.78,0:14:37.27,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone of you is my most precious family.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.50,0:14:39.40,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.87,0:14:44.26,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.16,0:14:47.57,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,What a beautiful ring to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.63,0:14:50.06,Default,Miriam,0000,0000,0000,,It's an impressionable and refreshing tone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.62,0:14:52.84,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,We made too many of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.04,0:14:56.36,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,These are for everyone at Oasis.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.94,0:15:02.03,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Miriam. These two are your cat and brother's share.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.20,0:15:03.74,Default,Miriam,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.45,0:15:10.00,Default,Miriam,0000,0000,0000,,Both of them will surely be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.00,0:15:28.49,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Miriam? {So she also is a automaton}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.42,0:15:31.63,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Miriam-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:36.77,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Miriam-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.93,0:15:38.74,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Miriam! Miriam!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.79,0:15:40.46,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Miriam!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.67,0:15:44.79,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Papa, that comfortable feeling of her is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.04,0:15:49.93,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,The commotion just now, did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.10,0:15:52.41,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Carina, Nina, Miriam is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.16,0:15:55.24,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Nina, contact the hospital immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.44,0:15:55.97,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.37,0:15:57.71,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,No need for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:00.30,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Garnet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.18,0:16:03.86,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like something troublesome has occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.13,0:16:06.33,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, let's take her to the hospital right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.03,0:16:08.64,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,I told you already, there's no need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.93,0:16:09.47,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.70,0:16:11.33,Default,Nina,0000,0000,0000,,Useless... Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.47,0:16:14.49,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,Don't panic, it's not as if she can't be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.23,0:16:16.32,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,About this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.96,0:16:18.11,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.91,0:16:21.24,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,Right on time. It's better for her to take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.80,0:16:24.09,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, no one is around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.91,0:16:26.31,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Agnes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.40,0:16:27.30,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.30,0:16:29.88,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,It's urgent, hurry! Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:31.03,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.86,0:16:38.01,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Miriam.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.62,0:16:51.74,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Say, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.06,0:16:53.53,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.56,0:16:55.66,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,We were all celebrating the completion of the bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.80,0:16:57.66,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Suddenly, Miriam collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.14,0:17:01.45,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,Leicester, have you realized yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.72,0:17:03.71,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,So that child is also one...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.03,0:17:04.39,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.93,0:17:08.70,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Agnes, how's Miriam doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.60,0:17:13.46,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,For now she's fine, Nina-san is looking after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.34,0:17:16.61,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,But everyone, listen to what I have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.88,0:17:22.89,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Will Miriam be alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.91,0:17:26.87,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, let's talk about that first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:32.38,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,The Miriam now... The condition of her core is extremely unstable. {That's why someone was looking for a core replacement...}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.91,0:17:35.28,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,The core?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.17,0:17:41.66,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,You see... Miriam is an automaton just like Minette.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.76,0:17:45.55,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,She's an automaton?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.86,0:17:47.73,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Leicester, you knew about it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.64,0:17:54.78,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow... I felt she was different from normal children.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:58.55,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Agnes, do you know Miriam-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.93,0:18:01.46,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I met her long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.85,0:18:05.56,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,But, the Miriam I knew was probably a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.22,0:18:09.62,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, a human turned into automaton?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.14,0:18:13.32,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,How... How could this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.68,0:18:16.03,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,This can be done, according to Aber-nii.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.39,0:18:18.17,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Aber-nii, that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.75,0:18:22.31,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Aber-nii and Miriam are blood-related siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.99,0:18:28.25,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,They are from the Roland family, who are successors of the lost automaton technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.63,0:18:30.49,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,They are indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.83,0:18:35.44,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,Our technology was passed onto the human society via such methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.62,0:18:40.97,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Initially, Miriam couldn't live long due to an illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:48.15,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So they relied on our dragon's superb technology?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.61,0:18:53.23,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,To use the body of an automaton to be free from the illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.55,0:18:57.10,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Then, why did she suddenly collapse now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.21,0:19:04.00,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,I've said this before, automata require large amounts of Ale to be activated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.40,0:19:10.41,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,Due to the unusual meteor showers in this world, the flow of Ale has lost its balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.94,0:19:14.51,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,To maintain the normal functioning of automata under such situations,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.64,0:19:18.55,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,a unique core that's able to control huge amounts of Ale is needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.57,0:19:21.49,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,A unique... core.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.04,0:19:25.77,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,Correct. Minette's core, the Anima Pearl. {mentioned in episode 02}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.87,0:19:30.06,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the reason why Aberdeen was targeting Minette.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.50,0:19:38.26,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there something else? Other than the Anima Pearl, similar to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.83,0:19:42.72,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,If it was so easy to find, Aber-nii would have long found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.72,0:19:43.90,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.11,0:19:48.02,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Those two didn't attack because they were searching for alternatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.12,0:19:49.30,Default,Agnes,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.66,0:19:50.59,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Garnet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.77,0:19:52.77,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,What will happen to Miriam?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.61,0:19:55.90,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,If this erratic behavior of Ale persists...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.69,0:20:00.50,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,That child's core will eventually stop functioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.03,0:20:08.15,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.32,0:20:10.54,Default,Garnet,0000,0000,0000,,I was just stating the facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.01,0:20:13.94,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,I hate this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.09,0:20:18.16,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,I hate this, I don't want this to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.65,0:20:19.63,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Minette.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.31,0:20:24.20,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Miriam is my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.80,0:20:26.22,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,I love her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.49,0:20:28.12,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,She's an important person!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.83,0:20:31.05,Default,Carina,0000,0000,0000,,Minette-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.18,0:20:35.42,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want it, I don't want this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:52.60,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.72,0:20:55.46,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, at such a time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.75,0:20:57.00,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.21,0:21:00.33,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,I really can't sleep because of Miriam's situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.72,0:21:01.78,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.71,0:21:04.78,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we have a chat for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.66,0:21:06.70,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.44,0:21:13.68,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Papa, what will happen to Miriam?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.32,0:21:16.92,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, Agnes and Nina-san are looking after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.40,0:21:18.33,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.42,0:21:20.33,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,But, if this goes on...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.62,0:21:21.55,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Minette.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.61,0:21:26.72,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody shares the same feeling of wanting to save Miriam-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.22,0:21:29.69,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Carina-san, Agnes and Nina-san; they feel the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.41,0:21:33.88,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,Chelsea-san and Nick-san will also help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.06,0:21:39.21,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,We may not know what's the best thing to do at the moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.09,0:21:43.76,Default,Lei,0000,0000,0000,,But as long everyone works together, we may be able to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.40,0:21:45.12,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.23,0:21:46.95,Default,Minette,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.05,0:21:51.17,Default,Nick,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
